{"tid":1919874,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民建聯、工聯會捲地勤騙案","createTime":"2020-03-11T05:25:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T07:01:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6da02e4a79d6132aa24cdd80a1b0df5e58abcc01","tid":1919874,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:25:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200311/GMXIKZEMHSAZ2AUIMMGNBUZORQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200311%2FGMXIKZEMHSAZ2AUIMMGNBUZORQ%2F&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=3e07d997\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200311%2FGMXIKZEMHSAZ2AUIMMGNBUZORQ%2F&h=a7d4a3aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200311/GMXIKZEMHSAZ2AUIMMGNBUZORQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n民建聯、工聯會捲地勤騙案<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200311/large/1583859519_82b2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200311%2Flarge%2F1583859519_82b2.gif&h=2e47b01c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葛珮帆<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民建聯及工聯會等保皇黨捲入地勤口罩騙案醜聞。懷疑受騙的王小姐（化名）從事貿易生意，其朋友X小姐（化名）2月16日透過通訊軟件與她接觸，聲稱手上有充足貨源，可協助訂購大量口罩，她隨即訂購2,000盒口罩，並於當日交付六位數字定金。其後王小姐在X慫恿下，於2月28日再向其訂購40,000盒口罩，並以現金付款200萬元。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：瞞疫禍延全球 巡場難挽威信<br />\n<br />\n騙徒疑借政黨過橋<br />\n<br />\n王小組與X小姐相識約逾十年，形容她性格「不嬲好好，係可信嘅人」，加上X在兜售過程中自稱曾擔任議員助理，認識有勢力人士，又稱民建聯、工聯會及明愛學校都有向其訂購口罩， 故不虞有詐，以大額現金向其付款。她過程中曾到X的公司簽署律師交件，X稱民建聯九龍東支部及工聯會陳婉嫻亦有簽署。<br />\n<br />\n至2月29日早上，X向王小姐稱因貨運延遲，需延遲兩日後才到貨，惟同日下午又再聯絡王，聲稱自己受騙，且已經到警署報案，並以「受害人」自居，叫王小姐亦盡快報警。及後王小姐向X表示，希望和她一起與民建聯開會，X此時突然改口提議向陳姓葵芳區議員求助，始引起王小姐疑心。王小姐經查詢後，發現民建聯沒有向X訂購口罩，而葵芳區亦沒有姓陳的區議員，才懷疑自己受騙，並於3月7日報警，王由始至終並沒有收到任何已訂購的口罩。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員葛珮帆指，已向黨內及工聯會陳婉嫻查詢，證實雙方均沒有與X訂購口罩或簽署文件，批評有人「拎政黨名呃人&hellip;&hellip;博取信任」。她懷疑這宗騙案與近日公佈的地勤騙案有關，X於2月29日聲稱受騙報案兩日後，警方隨即拘捕一名任職機場地勤的女子，而該女亦坦承所有罪行「攬晒上身」，並聲稱涉事金額已全部賭輸。<br />\n<br />\n■記者廖承志"},{"pid":"10bf9e09db496de2dd79c24bd26791180a5dd878","tid":1919874,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:26:11.000Z","msg":"【第貳拾玖期牆紙】 兄弟爬山<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1919455/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1919455/page/1</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=cea80068\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\nFB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F852wallpaper%2F&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=0ada0317\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/</a><br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hongkong_wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhongkong_wallpaper%2F&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=c98c1551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hongkong_wallpaper/</a><br />\nWEB: <a href=\"https://firsthand-news.web.app/wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffirsthand-news.web.app%2Fwallpaper%2F&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=bb157332\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://firsthand-news.web.app/wallpaper/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkDtkZf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkDtkZf.jpg&h=0ec8a28f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0384def5fb6f99287445471b557dc3bbe7dc1f62","tid":1919874,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:27:36.000Z","msg":"算啦，盲既都睇到禮義廉做緊comdom<br />\n<br />\n連口罩條生產線都益工聯會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7490bb57318aad72599d68cae3b8161527b1b65a","tid":1919874,"uid":268656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ypFLrjo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FypFLrjo.jpg&h=9a45f1e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11baf490ed8db3f3e4d4b68438941cdc455f64d4","tid":1919874,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:43:37.000Z","msg":"俾六位數訂金前唔查證?"},{"pid":"d0fec28c3a37a4c6783b43333a7466f9a9b5a579","tid":1919874,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T06:52:00.000Z","msg":"其後王小姐在X慫恿下，於2月28日再向其訂購40,000盒口罩，並以<span style=\"color: red;\">現金付款200萬元</span>。<br />\n<br />\n個劇本咁離奇嘅? 買口罩，買到好似電影中嘅毒犯咁，要用大量現金去交易?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686ac74d4b358c049561150a54defb539d04d380","tid":1919874,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0fec28c3a37a4c6783b43333a7466f9a9b5a579","tid":1919874,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T06:52:00.000Z","msg":"其後王小姐在X慫恿下，於2月28日再向其訂購40,000盒口罩，並以<span style=\"color: red;\">現金付款200萬元</span>。<br />\n<br />\n個劇本咁離奇嘅? 買口罩，買到好似電影中嘅毒犯咁，要用大量現金去交易?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:01:07.000Z","msg":"唔乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}